<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="in-this-case">in this case</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.<strong>在这种情况下：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You may think of giving up study. In this case, just think it over before making the decision.
你可能会想要放弃学习。在这种情况下，你要认真思考一下再作决定。</p></div></div>